{"about_the_game":"Experience the fun and excitement of being a dragon <i>and</i> a wizard \u2013 Devastate your foes with breath weapons, tooth n\u2019 claw melee combat, and an arsenal of magic!<br><br>Grow in power as you play through more than 40 procedurally generated dungeon levels where no two games are the same!<br><br>Vanquish your enemies, hoard collected treasure, and become a master wizard to defeat the forces of darkness and save your world in \u2013 THE DRAGON APPRENTICE!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Spells and More Spells |</h2>Harness the power of Rune Magic to conquer your enemies with a library of spells, plus spell discovery and loot systems that allow a wider and more personalized range of heroic gameplay.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Free Flight |</h2>Take to the air to evade enemy fire, launch devastating aerial attacks, and feel the freedom of untethered flight!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Ragdoll Physics |</h2>Blast and bash your foes down stairways, over ledges, or into the abyss with Ragdoll Physics \u2014 vanquish your enemies in spectacular fashion!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Loading Tips |</h2>We understand that everyone could use a little help when picking up a new game, so we added a variety of tips and tricks to every loading screen to improve your experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Backstory Bits |</h2>When the evil arch-litch, the BONE KING\u2122, and his Infernal Army launch a surprise assault on the Village of Ember, the Master Wizard Alvis Jarl banishes the undead battle-mage and his horde to wander Alvis\u2019s labyrinth of magical dungeons hidden deep within a mysterious alternate dimension known as the Netherealm. However, when Alvis hears that the dark wizard possesses an unhatched dragon\u2019s egg, he realizes he\u2019s played right into the BONE KING\u2019s plans to gain access to the hidden realm and perform a ritual that will give the dark one absolute power over the seven Cosmic Forces. Desperately needing to contain this threat, but weakened by battle, the wizard reluctantly takes on the fledgling dragon, Frigg, as his apprentice and charges her with clearing out the dungeons and dispatching this evil force once and for all.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Feed Me!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1666600/835950656e0f9fe8257190c21cfba653daa7773b.jpg"}],"total":1},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1677964031","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666600/page.bg.jpg?t=1677964031","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666600/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1677964031","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666600/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1677964031","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Experience the fun and excitement of being a dragon <i>and</i> a wizard \u2013 Devastate your foes with breath weapons, tooth n\u2019 claw melee combat, and an arsenal of magic!<br><br>Grow in power as you play through more than 40 procedurally generated dungeon levels where no two games are the same!<br><br>Vanquish your enemies, hoard collected treasure, and become a master wizard to defeat the forces of darkness and save your world in \u2013 THE DRAGON APPRENTICE!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Spells and More Spells |</h2>Harness the power of Rune Magic to conquer your enemies with a library of spells, plus spell discovery and loot systems that allow a wider and more personalized range of heroic gameplay.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Free Flight |</h2>Take to the air to evade enemy fire, launch devastating aerial attacks, and feel the freedom of untethered flight!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Ragdoll Physics |</h2>Blast and bash your foes down stairways, over ledges, or into the abyss with Ragdoll Physics \u2014 vanquish your enemies in spectacular fashion!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Loading Tips |</h2>We understand that everyone could use a little help when picking up a new game, so we added a variety of tips and tricks to every loading screen to improve your experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">| Backstory Bits |</h2>When the evil arch-litch, the BONE KING\u2122, and his Infernal Army launch a surprise assault on the Village of Ember, the Master Wizard Alvis Jarl banishes the undead battle-mage and his horde to wander Alvis\u2019s labyrinth of magical dungeons hidden deep within a mysterious alternate dimension known as the Netherealm. However, when Alvis hears that the dark wizard possesses an unhatched dragon\u2019s egg, he realizes he\u2019s played right into the BONE KING\u2019s plans to gain access to the hidden realm and perform a ritual that will give the dark one absolute power over the seven Cosmic Forces. Desperately needing to contain this threat, but weakened by battle, the wizard reluctantly takes on the fledgling dragon, Frigg, as his apprentice and charges her with clearing out the dungeons and dispatching this evil force once and for all.","developers":["PNUMIA Entertainment"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666600/header.jpg?t=1677964031","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"'The Dragon Apprentice' Copyright \u00a9 2016, Robert L Davidson III. All Rights Reserved.","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> <br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> <br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> <br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> <br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes: